metadata.name: Benedict Cumberbatch
metadata.description:
It is a week before the first series of Sherlock is aired in 2010, and I'm invited to Benedict's flat to photograph him for a personal project I'm working on. 

He throws on a shirt, puts some bread in the toaster, and we chat and shoot over breakfast and coffee.
